name: Suffocation
description:
It's a digital piece by Mrs M.Heydari as a member of Sepas art group.

Extremist and rotten beliefs kill the souls of Afghan women.
They must be suffocated with all cruelty and not breathe and have no right to protest.
I'm talking about women whose names are equivalent to miracles
I'm talking about helpless Afghan girls and women
They feel
They are kind
They do not sit back
And she wants the love of society.

"My Land" is one of the most famous and nostalgic Afghan music made about freedom that has been used in this piece.

It's for Afghan girls,wishing them freedom.
